import "./about.css" import Feynman from "../../../src/img/feynman.png" const about = () => { return (

About Me

I am currently a 3rd year Physics student with a minor in Computer Science, Chemistry and Economics at the University of Windsor.


In my Physics research position supervised by Dr. Rangan, we work on evaluating the interaction between light and matter at the nanoscale and the control of this interaction. Also, I have led teams in creating Python programming projects for research purposes. Currently I am working on learning and applying my knowledge in programming quantum computers.


In my Chemistry research position supervised by Dr. Trant, we are currently working on the design and synthesis of multifunctional nanocomposites for biological imaging.


In my free time, I volunteer at Newton's Taekwon-do as a 2nd degree black belt. I developed effective interpersonal and communication skills through leading group trainings, various open houses and events.

) } export default about
